      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't feel like an achievement though. it feels like a massive lie. i was supposed to be the one who made it, the one who provided for everyone. instead, i'm just a burden. every time i close my eyes i just see the bank statements and my parents' faces. it's like there's no way out of this version of me. i just want the feeling of being a failure to stop. it's constant.",
